data.description: Roof to be installed with proceeds!!!This beautiful 4 bedroom 2 bath home, in Holley by the Sea, is ready for you. Sitting on one of the most beautiful lots in the neighborhood, with endless possibilities. Add a pool, a casita or both. Beautifully landscaped and manicured. Ample parking in the large driveway pulling into a two car garage. Large primary bedroom opens to patio overlooking the backyard, enjoy your coffee while sitting and relaxing every morning. Plenty of room for an RV or Boat parking within the large privacy fence. Enjoy shopping, the most beautiful beaches, and golf. Minutes from Hurlburt field and a short distance to Eglin. Thirty minute trip to Pensacola, 25 min to Fort Walton Beach, with a 45 minute trip to Destin. Welcome Home!!! Home does not have a refrigerator that conveys, roof will be installed after clear to close is received.
